Privacy Policy for WhatsApp Sender
Effective Date: December 31, 2024

Your Privacy Matters to Us
At WhatsApp Sender, operated by Night Co, we prioritize your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle the information you provide while using our app.

1. Information We Collect
We do not collect, store, or share any personal information from users. The app operates locally on your device and does not send data to any external servers.

2. How the App Works
Input Data: The phone numbers and messages you input in the app are only used to facilitate sending messages via WhatsApp.
No Storage: The app does not save or retain any phone numbers, messages, or related data.
No Tracking: We do not track or monitor your activity within the app.
3. Permissions Required
The app may require the following permissions for its functionality:

Access to Phone Call Logs: To allow easy selection of numbers from your call history.
Internet Access: To open WhatsApp and send messages directly.
These permissions are solely used to enhance your experience and are not used to collect or store data.

4. Third-Party Services
This app uses WhatsApp Messenger to send messages. By using this app, you agree to WhatsApp’s terms of service and privacy policy. Please review their policies to understand how your data is handled when using their platform.

5. Data Security
Since no data is stored or transmitted by our app, there is no risk of data breaches or unauthorized access to your information through our app.

6. Children’s Privacy
Our app is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected here with an updated effective date. Please review this page periodically to stay informed about how we protect your privacy.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how the app operates, please contact us at:

Email: nightxnight00
Account Holder: Night Co
Thank you for using WhatsApp Sender!
